  "texts": [
    "However, articles have the higher citation impact (17.24) to conference papers, and almost half of the articles (48%) are open access while only 16% of the conference paper are open access.",
    "Surprisingly, a high proportion (60%) of the review papers are open access.",
    "In terms of citation, it is worth stating that conference reviews are non-citable documents.",
    "Figure 2 shows the distribution of publications by document type across the years.",
    "The plot shows that in recent time, articles emerged as the highest publication document type."
  ]
}